# Geospatial Comparison - Project Structure

## Overview

Next.js app comparing GeoJSON vs PMTiles map loading performance on Mapbox GL JS.

## Directory Structure

```
geospatial-comparison/
├── app/
│   ├── api/pmtiles/[filename]/route.ts   # PMTiles range-request API
│   ├── globals.css
│   ├── layout.tsx
│   └── page.tsx
├── components/
│   ├── GeoJSONMap.tsx        # Map component loading GeoJSON
│   ├── MapCard.tsx           # Reusable card wrapper for map + metrics
│   ├── MapComparison.tsx     # Main comparison layout
│   ├── MapErrorOverlay.tsx   # Shared error overlay for maps
│   ├── PerformanceMetrics.tsx # Metrics table and network simulation
│   └── PMTilesMap.tsx        # Map component loading PMTiles
├── hooks/
│   └── useMapboxMap.ts       # Shared map setup: token check, init, error, cleanup
├── lib/
│   ├── format.ts             # formatLoadTime, formatNumber
│   ├── map-config.ts         # MAP_STYLE, MAP_CENTER, MAP_ZOOM
│   └── metrics-helpers.ts    # computeMetricDiff, computeLoadTimeByNetwork, NETWORK_SPEEDS
├── public/
│   └── data/
│       ├── sample.geojson
│       └── sample.pmtiles
├── types/
│   ├── map.ts                # MapMetrics interface
│   └── mapbox-pmtiles.d.ts
└── structure.mdc
```

## Key Dependencies

- **mapbox-gl**: Map rendering
- **mapbox-pmtiles**: PMTiles source for Mapbox GL

## Data Flow

```
MapComparison
├── PerformanceMetrics (geojsonMetrics, pmtilesMetrics)
└── MapCard × 2
    ├── GeoJSONMap → setGeojsonMetrics
    └── PMTilesMap → setPmtilesMetrics
```
